        <s>They are laughing and enjoying the <choice><orig>diner</orig><reg>dinner</reg></choice> <choice><orig>untill</orig><reg>until</reg></choice> <ref target="b10gk3_1" type="character">King</ref> and his <choice><orig>Boys</orig><reg>boys</reg></choice> show up.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s><ref target="b10gk3_1" type="character">Maverick</ref> goes outside and violently argues with <ref target="b10gk3_1" type="character">King</ref>.</s>
        <s>Suddenly a police car drives in, <ref target="b10gk3_1" type="character">King</ref> drives away in a rush.</s>
        <s>One officer is black and one is white, they try to arrest <ref target="b10gk3_1" type="character">Maverick</ref> <choice><orig>untill</orig><reg>until</reg></choice> they realize <ref target="b10gk3_1" type="character">Starr</ref> is the witness.</s>
